### Overall

The codebase is structurally sound — no new panics, no new crypto misuse, no new unauthenticated handler paths. The fingerprinting leak in `fake_404_response` is the only new finding. The dev agents should prioritize closing the CTR-restart issues next as they're the highest-severity unresolved items.
